			)
		)
		(property "Description" "The Raspberry Pi Compute Module 4 CM4101016 single board computer is a powerful embedded solution featuring a 1.5GHz quad-core ARM Cortex-A72 processor and 1GB of RAM. Designed for versatility, it includes 28 digital I/O lines and supports multiple expansion interfaces such as I2C, SPI, and UART. With Gigabit Ethernet, USB 2.0, and various video output options including HDMI, CSI, DPI, and DSI, this SBC is ideal for a wide range of applications. Its compact size of 2.170 x 1.570 and operating temperature range of -20°C to 75°C make it suitable for both industrial and hobbyist projects."
			(at 78.74 88.9 0)
			(hide yes)
